animes.title: DARLING in the FRANXX
animes.description: While Hiro and Zero Two head to VIRM's home planet to defeat them, the rest of Squad 13 do their best to get life on Earth back on track.

animes.title: RADIANT
animes.description: Just when Seth decides to set out on a new journey after hearing what Yaga wrote in a letter to Alma, a massive number of Nemesis eggs rains down on Artemis Academy. The sorcerers of the city intercept them, but an egg they miss falls on an isolated island where Melie happens to be gathering mushrooms. Seth rushes to save her and fights the Nemesis that hatches from the egg, but its immense strength forces Seth into a corner, and his power once again goes berserk. Frightened by this inner power that he can't control, Seth makes a decision…

animes.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba
animes.description: As Tanjiro and the others are devoted to their rehabilitation training, the absolute master of the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji, gathers the Lower Ranks of the Twelve Kizuki. The demons, too, are preparing to make their next move. As training draws to a close, Tanjiro has improved to the point where he can fight on equal terms with Kanao. Just then, he receives word of a new mission from his Kasugai Crow.

animes.title: Lucky Star
animes.description: The school’s cultural festival brings all the girls together to work on a group cheer routine!

animes.title: Sailor Moon Crystal
animes.description: Death Phantom radiates an enormous dark power. Sailor Moon and Sailor Chibi Moon take a stand and release the power of the "Legendary Silver Crystal".

animes.title: Fire Force
animes.description: Before being discharged from the hospital, Shinra is visited by Captain Burns, who offers to tell him all about the fire that happened 12 years ago, but only if Shinra can demonstrate that he is strong enough to hear the whole truth.

animes.title: Eden of the East
animes.description: As missiles fill the skies above Japan once more, Takizawa must rush to prevent a catastrophe far greater than Careless Monday. He has the resources - but does he have enough time?

animes.title: Terror in Resonance
animes.description: Tokyo is in a state of emergency as the country readies itself for the atomic bomb explosion. Will the mystery of Sphinx finally be solved?

animes.title: Dances with the Dragons
animes.description: Gayus thinks back to the old days, when he was a still rash, inexperienced Jushikiist who hadn’t yet let learned to trust others.

animes.title: Fuuka
animes.description: Yuu wrote an original song in an attempt to bring Fuuka back to the band, but she persistently refused to meet with him. Now, as their growing popularity online has earned the attention of the HEDGEHOGS members, they've been invited to play at a live club again. The members have no choice but to practice their new song with no vocalist, but Yuu still isn't willing to give up. Can he get his feelings through to Fuuka?

animes.title: Shinobi no Ittoki
animes.description: Though Ittoki has set out to settle things with Kidou alone, Tokisada and Kousetsu rush to join him. Kidou has sent his full force to destroy Iga village. The final battle is about to begin.

animes.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN
animes.description: The Cursed Wombs: Death Paintings, Eso and Kechizu, face off against Itadori and Kugisaki, but the two begin to rot after they're bathed in the blood of Eso and Kechizu. Driven into a corner, Kugisaki hammers a nail into herself to activate Resonance and start a game of chicken with the brothers. Itadori refuses to stop and continues to attack Kechizu, but-- This whole mission began with one of Ryomen Sukuna's Fingers, so will Itadori, Kugisaki, and Fushiguro ultimately make it home to Jujutsu Tech safely?

animes.title: Chainsaw Man
animes.description: Sawatari sends the "Ghost Devil" after Hayakawa, and he's nearly killed before the "Ghost Devil" stops and hands him a cigarette with a message from Himeno. The words inside give Hayakawa the strength to kill the “Ghost Devil” and capture Sawatari.Meanwhile, Denji heads into his rematch with Samurai Sword. With a pull of the starter on his chest, he transforms into Chainsaw Man.And now, the last battle between Chainsaw Man and Samurai Sword has finally begun…

animes.title: Ningen Fushin: Adventurers Who Don't Believe in Humanity Will Save the World
Classroom of the Elite
animes.description: Ibuki has stolen the key card, and Horikita's condition has deteriorated. Over Horikita's objections, Ayanokoji forces her to drop out.

animes.title: Code Geass
animes.description: With Cornelia at his mercy, Lelouch seeks answers about his mother’s death. Suddenly, C.C. tells him that Nunnally has been kidnapped and that he must leave. Without Zero in the battle, can the Black Knights survive? Or will it all end with Suzaku’s vengeance?

animes.title: Play It Cool, Guys
animes.description: "Hayate and Takayuki have come to the stadium to cheer Shun on in his handball tournament, but for some reason Shun's friend Souma is missing. It turns out that he went onto the wrong train… Meanwhil Shun is really fired up about winning as much as possible to prolong being together in a team with his teammates who will retire after this event, but the hype backfires and he can't quite perform right…"

animes.title: Dr. STONE
animes.description: Senku and the kingdom learns of a mysterious disc left behind by his father and the other astronauts. They use their newfound technology to bring it to life.

animes.title: The Rising of the Shield Hero
animes.description: It turns out that Glass, like L'arc, is also a hero from other world. Naofumi barely fights off their combo attacks and then corners Glass in a one-on-one battle, but is then faced with an all-important question: does he truly wish to protect this world?

animes.title: Uzaki-chan Wants to Hang Out!
animes.description: Uzaki reminisces about her time with Sakurai in high school, then cooks up a scheme to see what he's like when he's drunk as summer comes to an end.
